<div dir="ltr">dear All,<div>sorry for your time. I have found the solution:</div><div><br></div><div><div style="font-size:12.7272720336914px"><div>  icount=1</div><div>  DO iCPU=0,MPI%nCPU-1</div><div>     IF(iCPU.NE.MPI%rank)THEN</div><div>        iTag=iCPU</div><div>        CALL MPI_ISEND(Ndata2send(iCPU),1,MPI_INTEGER,iCPU,iTag,MPI_COMM_WORLD,send_request(icount),MPI%iErr)</div><div>        icount=icount+1</div><div>     ENDIF</div><div>  ENDDO</div><div><br></div><div>  icount=1</div><div>  DO iCPU=0,MPI%nCPU-1</div><div>     IF(iCPU.NE.MPI%rank)THEN</div><div>        iTag=iCPU</div><div>        CALL MPI_IRECV(Ndata2recv(iCPU),1,MPI_INTEGER,iCPU,<span style="font-size:12.7272720336914px"><i>MPI%rank</i></span>,MPI_COMM_WORLD,recv_request(icount),MPI%iErr)</div><div>        icount=icount+1</div><div>     ENDIF</div><div>  ENDDO</div></div><div style="font-size:12.7272720336914px"><br></div><div style="font-size:12.7272720336914px"><br></div><div style="font-size:12.7272720336914px"><div><i> CALL MPI_WAITALL(3,send_request,send_status_list,MPI%iErr)</i></div><div><i> CALL MPI_WAITALL(3,recv_request,recv_status_list,MPI%iErr)</i></div><div><i><br></i></div><div>hoping this could help others</div><div>thanks for your time</div></div></div><div class="gmail_extra"><br></div></div>

